    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Breaching Harkon</strong> 是一款节奏紧凑的俯视角 <strong>Roguelike</strong> 射击游戏，拥有清晰的像素画面和现代化的枪战体验。打造完全<strong>失控</strong>的武器组合，巧妙周旋于致命敌人之间，并在战况过热时使用你的<strong>防暴盾牌</strong>存活下来。[／p]</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器与配件</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>65种以上强力升级</strong>，全面强化你的每一次挑战。从简单的装填速度提升，到让武器发射真正的激光。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>专业商人</strong>会随机出现，每位都提供<strong>传奇级</strong>装备与升级。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁<strong>酒保</strong>后，可获得临时增益效果，例如：<strong>无限弹药。</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103290/extras/ce9636436be07c9038e10d8349d19c53.poster.avif?t=1771976137\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103290/extras/ce9636436be07c9038e10d8349d19c53.webm?t=1771976137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103290/extras/ce9636436be07c9038e10d8349d19c53.mp4?t=1771976137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战<strong>5个危险区域</strong>！从<strong>走私场地</strong>和<strong>地下赌场</strong>到<strong>行驶中的列车</strong>。每个地点都拥有独特的敌人、危险机制和首领。关卡为半随机生成，手工打造的房间在每次挑战中都会以不同方式排列，带来无限重玩价值。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103290/extras/51101f61d6235f0f2296974e55a416e0.poster.avif?t=1771976137\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103290/extras/51101f61d6235f0f2296974e55a416e0.webm?t=1771976137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103290/extras/51101f61d6235f0f2296974e55a416e0.mp4?t=1771976137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Victor Harkon</strong> 通过<strong>财富</strong>、<strong>机器</strong>和<strong>冷酷武力</strong>统治着这个国家，但当他绑架你的女儿时，这场战争变得私人化。你与一家敌对的<strong>私人军事公司</strong>联手，逐层摧毁他的帝国，一步步逼近，直到在你与夺走她的那个人之间再无任何阻碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103290/extras/ab847a4bb2ba56e8dc4442c1e95a4191.poster.avif?t=1771976137\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103290/extras/ab847a4bb2ba56e8dc4442c1e95a4191.webm?t=1771976137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103290/extras/ab847a4bb2ba56e8dc4442c1e95a4191.mp4?t=1771976137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
